00:09:19.236 --> 00:09:21.349
So it now has 15 pants.

00:09:21.349 --> 00:09:23.471
Once again, it, too, is in a point

00:09:23.471 --> 00:09:25.635
beyond its production possibilities curve.

00:09:25.635 --> 00:09:29.064
It would not have been able
to get here without the trade.

00:09:29.064 --> 00:09:31.474
So they are both better off.

00:09:31.474 --> 00:09:33.994
So the key thing, the key
takeaway from this video

00:09:33.994 --> 00:09:37.226
