comparative advantage is valuable,

00:09:37.226 --> 00:09:38.712
once again, making all the assumptions

00:09:38.712 --> 00:09:41.208
for these simplified economic models,

00:09:41.208 --> 00:09:44.309
because we can calculate
out opportunity cost

00:09:44.309 --> 00:09:45.908
